After some negotiation, he agreed to 25 000 and 4 more meetings each worth of 20 000. A loan-shark was after him so he offered me to fuck him regularly. Too bad for him that I´m only interested in fresh and new asses. He will have to offer himself for the rest of the debt elsewhere.
title: Debt Dandy 163
